    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Hill top resorts and places of refuge, especially in Asia, built by colonial administrators as an escape from the hot climates or politally unstable conditions.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
